title: #92Noon: The NFL Free Agency Frenzy Continues!
description: Show kicks off with Ben Leber in studio for most of first hour, then Matt Birk calls in from the road. Gleeman in studio midway through, then former league exec Michael Lombardi is in the mix during the final hour!
